Class.name: Custom.SWARH.HIPS.ws.v2.q1.CdaDocumentDetails
Class.Description: <summary> CDA Document Details DTO. This object represents details about a clinical document that has been created by HIPS. </summary> Created from: http://sahipsh00.swarh.net:50500/HIPSServer_TEST/HIPS.Service.PCEHRService.svc?xsd=xsd14

Property.name: Document
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the CDA document. </summary>

Property.name: DocumentId
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the document identifier used when creating the CDA document. </summary>

Property.name: DocumentSetId
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the document set identifier used when creating the CDA document. </summary>

Property.name: Mrn
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the MRN number of the patient at the hospital that is specified in the patient identifier. If the MRN was auto-generated by HIPS then that value (which is based on a GUID) will be returned, otherwise it will be the MRN that was passed in the HL7 message to the Database Loader. </summary>

Property.name: PatientIdentifier
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets a patient identifier of the same type that was specified in the request. </summary>
